ClausePropertyAddDesc: Add a new property to the revision rule clause. The change to the clause is restricted to the modified revision rule. The modified revision rule is available only to the current user.
RevisionRuleClauseUpDesc: Move up the the order of execution of the selected clause. The change is restricted to the modified revision rule. The modified revision rule is available only to the current user.
RevisionRuleClauseDownDesc: Move down the order of execution of the selected clause. The change is restricted to the modified revision rule. The modified revision rule is available only to the current user.
RevisionRuleClauseAddDesc: Add a new clause to the revision rule.  The change is restricted to the modified revision rule. The modified revision rule is available only to the current user.
RevisionRuleClauseDeleteDesc: Remove the selected clauses from the revision rule. The change is restricted to the modified revision rule. The modified revision rule is available only to the current user.
RevisionRuleAdminDesc: Open the Revision Rule panel to view and modify selected revision rule definition.
ClausePropertyRemoveDesc: Remove the property from the revision rule clause. The change to the clause is restricted to the modified revision rule. The modified revision rule is available only to the current user.
ClausePropertyReplaceDesc: Replace the property with another one in the revision rule clause. The change to the clause is restricted to the modified revision rule. The modified revision rule is available only to the current user.
